Download and install [JDK].
Install IDE ([Netbeans IDE] or IntelliJ)
Clone the provided [AsteroidsFX] repository from GitHub
Open the“AsteroidsFX”project in the IDE.
Build the project from the root folder with the Maven command :  “mvn clean install.”
Run the project from the root folder with the Maven command :  “mvn exec:exec”
Implement the Bullet system for the Player component.
Implement an enemy spaceship in the project.  The enemy spaceship should shot and move randomly.